description: Demolition of all the buildings on the site apart from two facades of the building fronting Hackney Road; erection of two courtyard buildings of part 5, 6, 8 and 9 storeys to provide 188 residential units (C3 use) and 90.6 sqm (GIA) of flexible commercial/community floorspace (A1 and/or A2/or A3 and/or A4 and/or B1 and/or D1 and/or D2 and/or 'Community Enterprise' use); The creation of a new shared surface link between Kay Street and Haggerston Park; A shared surface street to the north of the development allowing access to basement parking for 30 cars; and associated highways and landscaping works.
